To create REACT app I used this methods

On your computer go to Run-> type npm install -g create-react-app
(This will install npm once globally)

To create a folder by the name of our react app

Go to run-> type create-react-app sign_form(name of the folder)

Go to node.ja command prompt 
type cd sign_form
then inside sign_form install (react and bootstrap table)
type npm install react-> when its done
type npm install react-bootstrap-table

Now we are ready to use the react app.

what we have done as index.html goes to public folder inside sign_form folder
inside sign_form folder add .css part and .js part.

When everything is ready go to node.ja command prompt
type cd sign_form click enter
type npm start

Here we go 
